<p>It was not sucking the nipples of al-Lat, but Abu Bakr told him to suk the clitoris of al-Lat. </p>
<p>Even worse, the Spanish version replaces Abu Bakr’s words with entirely different words. The passage is translated as “Abû Bakr le dijo: ‘Húndete en la ignominia!’” translates into English as “Abu Bakr said to him: ‘<strong>Bury yourself in ignominy</strong>!’”</p>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718im_/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156138.jpg" width="998" height="718" /></p>
<p>But however, we have one honest translator in the form of Michael Fishbein (a non-Muslim). He translated it absolutely correctly:</p>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718im_/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156094.jpg?w=1100" sizes="(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px" srcset="https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718im_/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156094.jpg?w=1100 1100w, https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718im_/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156094.jpg?w=150 150w, https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718im_/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156094.jpg?w=300 300w, https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718im_/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156094.jpg?w=768 768w, https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718im_/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156094.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718im_/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156094.jpg 1980w" alt="wp-1581279156094.jpg" width="1000" data-attachment-id="1180" data-permalink="https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718/https://theislamissue.wordpress.com/wp-1581279156094/" data-orig-file="https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156094.jpg" data-orig-size="1980,1373" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="wp-1581279156094.jpg" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://web.archive.org/web/20201122233718/https://theislamissue.files.wordpress.com/2020/02/wp-1581279156094.jpg?w=300"